     5	#### See the user manual [here](https://manual.groundseg.app) for usage documentation
     6	
     7	GroundSeg is a software tool that helps users manage and access their multiple Urbit instances. 
     8	It simplifies the process of getting onto the Urbit network and provides a range of additional services 
     9	that enhance the functionality of the user's ship. With a [StarTram](https://www.nativeplanet.io/startram) 
    10	subscription, users can also access their Urbit ship remotely.
    11	
    12	Native Planet develops GroundSeg to run on our [dedicated Urbit-hosting home devices](https://www.nativeplanet.io)! 
    13	
    14	## Dependencies
    15	
    16	- `docker`
    17	- `systemd`
